{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":720,"text":"Every summer, my family and I\ntravel across the world,"},{"time":5440,"text":"3,000 miles away"},{"time":7320,"text":"to the culturally diverse\ncountry of India."},{"time":10760,"text":"Now, India is a country infamous\nfor its scorching heat and humidity."},{"time":15760,"text":"For me, the only relief from this heat\nis to drink plenty of water."},{"time":20920,"text":"Now, while in India,"},{"time":22440,"text":"my parents always remind me\nto only drink boiled or bottled water,"},{"time":27400,"text":"because unlike here in America,"},{"time":29680,"text":"where I can just turn on a tap\nand easily get clean, potable water,"},{"time":34480,"text":"in India, the water is often contaminated."},{"time":37440,"text":"So my parents have to make sure"},{"time":39360,"text":"that the water we drink is safe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42480,"text":"However, I soon realized"},{"time":44880,"text":"that not everyone is fortunate enough"},{"time":47560,"text":"to enjoy the clean water we did."},{"time":51160,"text":"Outside my grandparents' house\nin the busy streets of India,"},{"time":55400,"text":"I saw people standing in long lines"},{"time":58080,"text":"under the hot sun"},{"time":59800,"text":"filling buckets with water from a tap."},{"time":63360,"text":"I even saw children,"},{"time":65360,"text":"who looked the same age as me,"},{"time":68040,"text":"filling up these clear plastic bottles"},{"time":70440,"text":"with dirty water\nfrom streams on the roadside."},{"time":74880,"text":"Watching these kids"},{"time":76600,"text":"forced to drink water"},{"time":78760,"text":"that I felt was too dirty to touch"},{"time":81800,"text":"changed my perspective on the world."},{"time":85040,"text":"This unacceptable social injustice"},{"time":88600,"text":"compelled me to want to find a solution"},{"time":91680,"text":"to our world's clean water problem."},{"time":94840,"text":"I wanted to know\nwhy these kids lacked water,"},{"time":98120,"text":"a substance that is essential for life."},{"time":101000,"text":"And I learned that we are facing"},{"time":103280,"text":"a global water crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106720,"text":"Now, this may seem surprising,"},{"time":108560,"text":"as 75 percent of our planet\nis covered in water,"},{"time":112680,"text":"but only 2.5 percent\nof that is freshwater,"},{"time":116760,"text":"and less than one percent\nof Earth's freshwater supply"},{"time":120720,"text":"is available for human consumption."},{"time":123760,"text":"With rising populations,"},{"time":125480,"text":"industrial development\nand economic growth,"},{"time":128479,"text":"our demand for clean water is increasing,"},{"time":131280,"text":"yet our freshwater resources\nare rapidly depleting."},{"time":135840,"text":"According to the\nWorld Health Organization,"},{"time":138480,"text":"660 million people in our world"},{"time":142400,"text":"lack access to a clean water source."},{"time":145960,"text":"Lack of access to clean water\nis a leading cause of death"},{"time":149280,"text":"in children under the age of five\nin developing countries,"},{"time":152320,"text":"and UNICEF estimates that 3,000 children"},{"time":155800,"text":"die every day from\na water-related disease."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160280,"text":"So after returning home\none summer in eighth grade,"},{"time":163680,"text":"I decided that I wanted\nto combine my passion"},{"time":166800,"text":"for solving the global water crisis"},{"time":168960,"text":"with my interest in science."},{"time":171440,"text":"So I decided that the best thing to do"},{"time":173600,"text":"would be to convert my garage\ninto a laboratory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181160,"text":"Actually, at first I converted\nmy kitchen into a laboratory,"},{"time":185040,"text":"but my parents didn't really approve\nand kicked me out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189400,"text":"I also read a lot of journal papers\non water-related research,"},{"time":193880,"text":"and I learned that currently\nin developing countries,"},{"time":196760,"text":"something called solar disinfection,"},{"time":199200,"text":"or SODIS, is used to purify water."},{"time":203000,"text":"In SODIS, clear plastic bottles\nare filled with contaminated water"},{"time":207840,"text":"and then exposed to sunlight\nfor six to eight hours."},{"time":211520,"text":"The UV radiation from the sun"},{"time":213560,"text":"destroys the DNA\nof these harmful pathogens"},{"time":217040,"text":"and decontaminates the water."},{"time":219880,"text":"Now, while SODIS is really easy to use\nand energy-efficient,"},{"time":223640,"text":"as it only uses solar energy,"},{"time":225960,"text":"it's really slow,"},{"time":227360,"text":"as it can take up to two days\nwhen it's cloudy."},{"time":230960,"text":"So in order to make\nthe SODIS process faster,"},{"time":234080,"text":"this new method called photocatalysis"},{"time":237400,"text":"has recently been used."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239640,"text":"So what exactly is this photocatalysis?"},{"time":242520,"text":"Let's break it down:"},{"time":243760,"text":"\"photo\" means from the sun,"},{"time":245440,"text":"and a catalyst is something\nthat speeds up a reaction."},{"time":249040,"text":"So what photocatalysis is doing"},{"time":251240,"text":"is it's just speeding up\nthis solar disinfection process."},{"time":255400,"text":"When sunlight comes in\nand strikes a photocatalyst,"},{"time":258760,"text":"like TiO2, or titanium dioxide,"},{"time":262400,"text":"it creates these\nreally reactive oxygen species,"},{"time":265840,"text":"like superoxides, hydrogen peroxide\nand hydroxyl radicals."},{"time":270920,"text":"These reactive oxygen species"},{"time":272840,"text":"are able to remove bacteria and organics"},{"time":275760,"text":"and a whole lot of contaminants\nfrom drinking water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279920,"text":"But unfortunately,\nthere are several disadvantages"},{"time":283160,"text":"to the way photocatalytic SODIS\nis currently deployed."},{"time":287640,"text":"See, what they do is they take\nthe clear plastic bottles"},{"time":290800,"text":"and they coat the inside\nwith this photocatalytic coating."},{"time":295200,"text":"But photocatalysts like titanium dioxide"},{"time":298520,"text":"are actually commonly used in sunscreens"},{"time":301240,"text":"to block UV radiation."},{"time":303320,"text":"So when they're coated\non the inside of these bottles,"},{"time":306200,"text":"they're actually blocking\nsome of the UV radiation"},{"time":309000,"text":"and diminishing the efficiency\nof the process."},{"time":312560,"text":"Also, these photocatalytic coatings"},{"time":314720,"text":"are not tightly bound\nto the plastic bottle,"},{"time":317600,"text":"which means they wash off,\nand people end up drinking the catalyst."},{"time":322520,"text":"While TiO2 is safe and inert,"},{"time":325200,"text":"it's really inefficient\nif you keep drinking the catalyst,"},{"time":327960,"text":"because then you have\nto continue to replenish it,"},{"time":330360,"text":"even after a few uses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332440,"text":"So my goal was\nto overcome the disadvantages"},{"time":335720,"text":"of these current treatment methods"},{"time":337760,"text":"and create a safe, sustainable,"},{"time":340040,"text":"cost-effective and eco-friendly\nmethod of purifying water."},{"time":345120,"text":"What started off as an eighth grade\nscience fair project"},{"time":348200,"text":"is now my photocatalytic composite\nfor water purification."},{"time":353440,"text":"The composite combines\ntitanium dioxide with cement."},{"time":357840,"text":"The cement-like composite can be formed\ninto several different shapes,"},{"time":361840,"text":"which results in an extremely\nversatile range of deployment methods."},{"time":366160,"text":"For example, you could create a rod"},{"time":368240,"text":"that can easily be placed\ninside water bottles for individual use"},{"time":372560,"text":"or you could create a porous filter\nthat can filter water for families."},{"time":377800,"text":"You can even coat the inside\nof an existing water tank"},{"time":381240,"text":"to purify larger amounts of water"},{"time":383120,"text":"for communities\nover a longer period of time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387640,"text":"Now, over the course of this,"},{"time":389600,"text":"my journey hasn't really been easy."},{"time":392080,"text":"You know, I didn't have access\nto a sophisticated laboratory."},{"time":395480,"text":"I was 14 years old when I started,"},{"time":399000,"text":"but I didn't let my age deter me"},{"time":401360,"text":"in my interest\nin pursuing scientific research"},{"time":404240,"text":"and wanting to solve\nthe global water crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407800,"text":"See, water isn't\njust the universal solvent."},{"time":411640,"text":"Water is a universal human right."},{"time":415160,"text":"And for that reason,"},{"time":416440,"text":"I'm continuing to work\non this science fair project from 2012"},{"time":420640,"text":"to bring it from the laboratory\ninto the real world."},{"time":423840,"text":"And this summer,\nI founded Catalyst for World Water,"},{"time":427320,"text":"a social enterprise aimed at catalyzing\nsolutions to the global water crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433280,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440240,"text":"Alone, a single drop of water\ncan't do much,"},{"time":444240,"text":"but when many drops come together,"},{"time":446680,"text":"they can sustain life on our planet."},{"time":450280,"text":"Just as water drops\ncome together to form oceans,"},{"time":453640,"text":"I believe that we all must come together"},{"time":456200,"text":"when tackling this global problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459080,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":460320,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":463840,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465200,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}